Subject: [PATCH 3/5] Fix curve25519-sha256 key exchange bug

https://github.com/Alexpux/MSYS2-packages/blob/master/openssh/curve25519-sha256.patch
---
 bufaux.c      |  5 ++++-
 compat.c      | 16 +++++++++++++++-
 compat.h      |  2 ++
 sshconnect2.c |  2 ++
 sshd.c        |  3 +++
 version.h     |  2 +-
 6 files changed, 27 insertions(+), 3 deletions(-)

